{"Id":482145,"Title":"咏苏守义妻齐氏","Dynasty":"明","Author":"陶安","Context":"幽燕之南，晋赵之疆。刀锄剑樵，其人劲强。安平故邑，村有新庄。懿彼贞女，曰齐之姜。来嫔于苏，功容并良。孝周舅姑，礼谨闺房。夫遘危疾，永诀在床。谓汝改适，怜其早孀。齐沥丹诚，执心孔刚。誓无辱身，宁甘自戕。夫目遄暝，妾命乃长。胡能独生？曷若偕亡？金石可朽，言弗忍忘。冈陵可移，义弗忍伤。九原当见，以死自明。永谢膏沐，魂离室堂。欲拯何及？举族悲惶。行高千古，事昭一乡。守宰嘉叹，宪使荐扬。旌命自天，门闾有光。断鼻执义，夏侯德彰。剔目示信，房卢性臧。谁能捐躯，同穴而藏？恒山郁苍，厥高莫量。烈烈令闻，能与之京？张侯戾学，称善洋洋。激励孝忠，增重纲常。作此雅歌，亘久弥芳。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"e97ba96f63a4d3a8c43c00746ec3aa7d","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6745614,"Sentence":"刀锄剑樵，其人劲强。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dāo chú jiàn qiáo ，jī rén jìn jiàng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6745615,"Sentence":"安平故邑，村有新庄。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"ān pǐng gù yì ，cūn yǒu xīn zhuāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6745616,"Sentence":"懿彼贞女，曰齐之姜。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yì bi zhēn nǚ ，yuē jì zhī jiāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6745617,"Sentence":"来嫔于苏，功容并良。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lái pǐn yú sū ，gōng róng bīng liáng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6745618,"Sentence":"孝周舅姑，礼谨闺房。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xiào zhōu jìu gū ，li jin guī fáng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6745619,"Sentence":"夫遘危疾，永诀在床。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fū gòu wēi jǐ ，yǒng jué zài chuáng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6745620,"Sentence":"谓汝改适，怜其早孀。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wèi rǔ gǎi kuò ，lián jī zǎo shuāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6745621,"Sentence":"齐沥丹诚，执心孔刚。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jì lì dān chéng ，zhǐ xīn kǒng gāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6745622,"Sentence":"誓无辱身，宁甘自戕。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pi